            <p>The KVH network can allow inbound applications or ports, (i.e. Microsoft Remote Desktop, VNC, SSH, http/https, IPsec and many more) Into your global public Internet address from anywhere on the Internet or it can allow access only from specific public Internet addresses that you provide.</p>
